    "id": "ex-wg-1",
    "cat": "waveguide",
    "title": "矩形波导 TE₁₀ 模截止与波导波长",
    "type": "计算",
    "problem": "空气填充矩形波导宽边 $a=22.86\\ \\mathrm{mm}$，窄边 $b=10.16\\ \\mathrm{mm}$（标准 WR-90）。工作频率 $f=10\\ \\mathrm{GHz}$。求 TE₁₀ 模截止频率 $f_c$、截止波长 $\\lambda_c$、波导波长 $\\lambda_g$，并判断该频率下能否单模传输。",
    "steps": [
      {
        "text": "TE₁₀ 模 $m=1,n=0$，由 $f_c=\\dfrac{1}{2\\sqrt{\\mu\\varepsilon}}\\sqrt{(m/a)^{2}+(n/b)^{2}}$，$n=0$ 时 $f_c=\\dfrac{c}{2a}$。",
        "latex": "f_c=\\frac{c}{2a}=\\frac{3\\times10^{8}}{2\\times 22.86\\times10^{-3}}\\approx 6.56\\times10^{9}\\ \\mathrm{Hz}=6.56\\ \\mathrm{GHz}"
      },
      {
        "text": "TE₁₀ 截止波长 $\\lambda_c=2a$。",
        "latex": "\\lambda_c=2a=2\\times 22.86=45.72\\ \\mathrm{mm}"
      },
      {
        "text": "工作频率 $f=10\\ \\mathrm{GHz}>f_c=6.56\\ \\mathrm{GHz}$，TE₁₀ 可传播。自由空间波长 $\\lambda_0=c/f$。",
        "latex": "\\lambda_0=\\frac{c}{f}=\\frac{3\\times10^{8}}{10^{10}}=30\\ \\mathrm{mm}"
      },
      {
        "text": "波导波长 $\\lambda_g=\\dfrac{\\lambda_0}{\\sqrt{1-(f_c/f)^{2}}}$。",
        "latex": "\\lambda_g=\\frac{30}{\\sqrt{1-(6.56/10)^{2}}}=\\frac{30}{\\sqrt{1-0.430}}=\\frac{30}{\\sqrt{0.570}}\\approx\\frac{30}{0.755}"
      },
      {
        "text": "得波导波长，大于自由空间波长（波导色散）。",
        "latex": "\\lambda_g\\approx 39.8\\ \\mathrm{mm}"
      },
      {
        "text": "判断单模：TE₂₀ 截止 $f_{c,20}=c/a=13.12\\ \\mathrm{GHz}>10\\ \\mathrm{GHz}$；TE₀₁ 截止 $f_{c,01}=c/(2b)=14.76\\ \\mathrm{GHz}>10\\ \\mathrm{GHz}$。故仅 TE₁₀ 传播，单模工作。",
        "latex": "f_{c,20}=13.12\\ \\mathrm{GHz}>f,\\ f_{c,01}=14.76\\ \\mathrm{GHz}>f\\ \\Rightarrow\\ \\text{单模 TE}_{10}"
      }
    ],
    "answer": "\\boxed{f_c\\approx 6.56\\ \\mathrm{GHz},\\quad \\lambda_c=45.72\\ \\mathrm{mm},\\quad \\lambda_g\\approx 39.8\\ \\mathrm{mm},\\quad \\text{TE}_{10}\\text{ 单模可传播}}",
    "related": [
      "wg-cutoff-f",
      "wg-cutoff-lambda",
      "wg-guide-lambda"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "ex-wg-2",
    "cat": "waveguide",
    "title": "无耗传输线的输入阻抗",
    "type": "计算",
    "problem": "无耗均匀传输线特性阻抗 $Z_0=50\\ \\Omega$，终端接负载 $Z_L=(50+j100)\\ \\Omega$，工作波长 $\\lambda$。求距负载 $l=\\lambda/8$ 处的输入阻抗 $Z_{\\text{in}}$。",
    "steps": [
      {
        "text": "无耗传输线输入阻抗公式 $Z_{\\text{in}}=Z_0\\dfrac{Z_L+jZ_0\\tan(\\beta l)}{Z_0+jZ_L\\tan(\\beta l)}$。",
        "latex": "Z_{\\text{in}}=Z_0\\,\\frac{Z_L+jZ_0\\tan(\\beta l)}{Z_0+jZ_L\\tan(\\beta l)}"
      },
      {
        "text": "$l=\\lambda/8$ 时 $\\beta l=\\dfrac{2\\pi}{\\lambda}\\cdot\\dfrac{\\lambda}{8}=\\dfrac{\\pi}{4}$，故 $\\tan(\\beta l)=1$。",
        "latex": "\\beta l=\\frac{\\pi}{4},\\quad \\tan(\\beta l)=1"
      },
      {
        "text": "代入数据：分子 $Z_L+jZ_0=(50+j100)+j50=50+j150$；分母 $Z_0+jZ_L=50+j(50+j100)=50-100+j50=-50+j50$。",
        "latex": "Z_{\\text{in}}=50\\times\\frac{50+j150}{-50+j50}"
      },
      {
        "text": "分子分母同乘分母的共轭 $(-50-j50)$ 化简。",
        "latex": "\\frac{50+j150}{-50+j50}=\\frac{(50+j150)(-50-j50)}{(-50)^{2}+50^{2}}=\\frac{-2500-j2500-j7500+7500}{5000}=\\frac{5000-j10000}{5000}=1-j2"
      },
      {
        "text": "代入得 $Z_{\\text{in}}$，含负虚部呈容性。",
        "latex": "Z_{\\text{in}}=50\\,(1-j2)=50-j100\\ \\Omega"
      }
    ],
    "answer": "\\boxed{Z_{\\text{in}}=(50-j100)\\ \\Omega}",
    "related": [
      "wg-z0-lossless"
    ]
  },
