    "title": "矩形谐振腔的谐振频率",
    "type": "计算",
    "problem": "空气填充矩形谐振腔尺寸 $a=2\\ \\mathrm{cm}$、$b=1\\ \\mathrm{cm}$、$d=3\\ \\mathrm{cm}$。求 $\\mathrm{TE}_{101}$ 模（$m=1,n=0,p=1$）的谐振频率 $f_{101}$。",
    "steps": [
      {
        "text": "矩形谐振腔谐振频率 $f_{mnp}=\\dfrac{1}{2\\sqrt{\\mu\\varepsilon}}\\sqrt{(m/a)^{2}+(n/b)^{2}+(p/d)^{2}}$，空气 $1/\\sqrt{\\mu\\varepsilon}=c$。",
        "latex": "f_{mnp}=\\frac{c}{2}\\sqrt{\\left(\\frac{m}{a}\\right)^{2}+\\left(\\frac{n}{b}\\right)^{2}+\\left(\\frac{p}{d}\\right)^{2}}"
      },
      {
        "text": "$\\mathrm{TE}_{101}$ 模 $m=1,n=0,p=1$，含 $n$ 的项消失。",
        "latex": "f_{101}=\\frac{c}{2}\\sqrt{\\left(\\frac{1}{a}\\right)^{2}+\\left(\\frac{1}{d}\\right)^{2}}"
      },
      {
        "text": "代入尺寸计算根号内之值。",
        "latex": "\\left(\\frac{1}{0.02}\\right)^{2}+\\left(\\frac{1}{0.03}\\right)^{2}=2500+1111=3611\\ \\mathrm{m^{-2}}"
      },
      {
        "text": "开方后代入 $c$。",
        "latex": "\\sqrt{3611}\\approx 60.1\\ \\mathrm{m^{-1}},\\quad f_{101}=\\frac{3\\times10^{8}}{2}\\times 60.1"
      },
      {
        "text": "得谐振频率。仅当激励频率等于某 $f_{mnp}$ 时腔内形成稳定驻波，偏离则响应急剧下降。",
        "latex": "f_{101}\\approx 9.01\\times10^{9}\\ \\mathrm{Hz}=9.01\\ \\mathrm{GHz}"
      }
    ],
    "answer": "\\boxed{f_{101}\\approx 9.01\\ \\mathrm{GHz}}",
    "related": [
      "wg-resonator",
      "wg-cutoff-f"
    ]
  }
]
